        "Tooltip": {
          "enUS": "The troops to which Nod belongs do not have the conventional third-level armament upgrade in the Koprulu sector, but instead have battlefield experience upgrades. <br/>Each Nod unit needs to kill units twice its own production value before it can advance. <br/>Level 1: Increase armor by 1 point. <br/>Level 2: Increase weapon damage by 15%. <br/>Level 3: Increase armor by 1 point and gain slow health recovery. <br/>If there are multiple Nod units nearby when a unit is killed, the experience gained by the killed unit will be divided equally. <br/>Each unit can be upgraded up to 3 times."
